data.description: WOW! Great ranch style home on a cul-de-sac in Chapel Hill! Home has been in the family for a long time!  Home has original hardwood floors and has been freshly painted. Kitchen has solid surface countertops w/ breakfast bar! Garage is finished and has a bump out workshop attached and side door that leads to the backyard, Brick courtyard, firepit, and storage shed! Home is not advertised for Rent.
